lead_paragraph: U.S. President Barack Obama met Hillary Clinton, his former secretary of state, on Wednesday but the White House declined to say whether they discussed her possible presidential candidacy in 2016.

headline.main: Obama, Hillary Clinton Meet at White House but Details Are Few
